774c83","tid":1139242,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8d612e91c9458d08100aeaa5a209605f99fa548","tid":1139242,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"917233e7761ed47d3d5027d5276e09074dd9360e","tid":1139242,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"所有反對飯民都係五毛  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa99a373fb2704779c9efb70c2b07864206a4d9","tid":1139242,"uid":29270,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"所有對泛民不利既人，毓民、關蛇、仇斯達、陳浩天等等<br />\n<br />\n全部變晒落水狗/冇人提，變晒阿塗阿塗咁叫<br />\n仇斯達大罵泛民請打手我唔信，依加冇得我唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cd1dbc523f1d1ac5511d92ebe395256926d339","tid":1139242,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8fa99a373fb2704779c9efb70c2b07864206a4d9","tid":1139242,"uid":29270,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"所有對泛民不利既人，毓民、關蛇、仇斯達、陳浩天等等<br />\n<br />\n全部變晒落水狗/冇人提，變晒阿塗阿塗咁叫<br />\n仇斯達大罵泛民請打手我唔信，依加冇得我唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"補充幾句，仲有幾件事反映有打手做事<br />\n1. 吳文遠籌款登蘋果，登報之前根本冇人討論，但有某批user不停嘗試炒起事件<br />\n2. 杜汶澤向來反泛民，時事台好少討論呢個人，一有拖糧醜聞就不停有人炒起"}]}